title: Tom’s Taco Bar is delightful
text:
I went to Tom’s Taco Bar expecting just another place to get an injection of tortillas, cheese, and meat.    
   
Lo and behold that is not the experience I had.   

They offer more than just delicious tacos; it's a culinary sanctuary where every bite feels like a spiritual awakening. From the moment you walk in, you're enveloped in the divine aroma of sizzling meats and spices. The first bite is a revelation, each flavor harmonizing perfectly to create a symphony of taste. With every taco, you're transported to a higher plane of gastronomic delight. Tom's Taco Bar isn't just a restaurant; it's a temple of flavor, where every visit feels like a religious experience.

title: Public Storage 130 Landing Court  Novato Ca
text:
What keeps this particular facility going is Josephine the property manager.
She really shines with business dealing at the site Always friendly, clear with instructions, willing to solve problems, finds an orange cart(by the way, they only have 2 for this oversized facility) plus she works with customers sudden price hikes! 
She also keeps the property and units exceptionally clean! 

Public Storage is fortunate to have Josephine in charge.
